===Etymology===
From {{etyl|my|en}} {{term|ဗမာ|tr=băma|lang=my}}, colloquial form of {{term|မြန်မာ|tr=myanma|lang=my}}; see {{term|Myanmar|lang=en}} for more.

===Pronunciation===
* {{audio|En-us-Burma.ogg|Audio (US)}}
* {{rhymes|ɜː(r)mə}}

===Proper noun===
{{en-proper noun}}

# [[Myanmar]]; a country in [[Southeast Asia]], on the west coast of the [[w:Indochina Peninsula|Indochina Peninsula]].

====Usage notes====
''Burma'' is a traditional name of [[Myanmar]], and was the official name until 1989.  It is still used to express disapproval of the military government which changed the name. See {{w|Names of Burma}} on Wikipedia.

